{"tid":1404812,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我呀媽係手足","createTime":"2019-08-04T06:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:55:50.000Z","uid":266632,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7ecaeb1e1388989aab1ffc47033d9de996bf811b","tid":1404812,"uid":266632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:11:57.000Z","msg":"呀媽啱啱睇緊鄺俊宇fb live<br />\n鄺：&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;而家呢2千幾個睇緊直播既手足&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n呀媽抬頭望住我：佢話睇緊直播既手足呀，我都係手足呀（燦爛笑）當下覺得呀媽真可愛，人地話手足佢就當自己係手足，但諗番其實好感動，因為佢真係手足，佢反修例以黎既反應完全喺我意料之外。<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個月佢經常喺fb刨新聞至凌晨，幾乎睇哂立場6月以黎所有live同記招，我放工番嚟仲同我重溫佢睇咗d乜，藍屍親戚喺whatsapp group嗌人小心暴徒，佢一睇到即刻打俾對方：你知唔知警察做咗d咩吖？佢夾埋黑社會打市民呀，元朗點點點，上環點點點，聽住佢瘋狂拋書包，一輪嘴up好多好多佢睇過既片同新聞，我真係嘴角笑到上耳仔，佢太令我自豪！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160ba4080eed6fd14c998428f1d34551f029a629","tid":1404812,"uid":109891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:13:45.000Z","msg":"媽媽好可愛"},{"pid":"8cb91022316b404c50fcd3f01bd9e6481a3b609d","tid":1404812,"uid":67168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"Proud of you!<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n8月5一齊罷工！"},{"pid":"8a7816dbc64a51f24d70881483064af827abcb0e","tid":1404812,"uid":263231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"教佢上埋連登"},{"pid":"eb31892016676af0c62de5b651ecae7ee1bf7c2d","tid":1404812,"uid":266632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8cb91022316b404c50fcd3f01bd9e6481a3b609d","tid":1404812,"uid":67168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"Proud of you!<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n8月5一齊罷工！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:43:14.000Z","msg":"佢話會呼應罷工呀<br />\n星期一唔煮飯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" cl